baolong_score = 0
for dict_i in baolong:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        baolong_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(baolong_score)

cangshan_score = 0
for dict_i in cangshan:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        cangshan_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(cangshan_score)

dongerhuan_score = 0
for dict_i in dongerhuan:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        dongerhuan_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(dongerhuan_score)

dongjiekou_score = 0
for dict_i in dongjiekou:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        dongjiekou_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(dongjiekou_score)

jinronjie_score = 0
for dict_i in jinronjie:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        jinronjie_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(jinronjie_score)

wusibei_score = 0
for dict_i in wusibei:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        wusibei_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
print(wusibei_score)

    {
        "href": "https://www.meituan.com/jiehun/193911896/",

wuyi_score = 0
for dict_i in wuyi:
    if dict_i['level'][0] != '暂无评分':
        wuyi_score += float(dict_i['level'][1].split('分')[0])
a = [baolong_score, cangshan_score, dongerhuan_score, dongjiekou_score, jinronjie_score, wusibei_score, wuyi_score]
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
 # 设置matplotlib正常显示中文
 # 生成画布
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 8), dpi=80)
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']
plt.rcParams['font.serif'] = ['SimHei']
name = ['宝龙万象城服饰','仓山万达服饰','东二环泰禾广场服饰','东街口服饰','金融街万达服饰','五四北泰禾广场服饰','五一广场服饰']
y=[a[0],a[1],a[2],a[3],a[4],a[5],a[6]]
x=range(len(name))
plt.bar(x,y,width=0.5, color=['b','r','g','y','c','m','y'])
plt.xticks(x,name)
plt.title='黄彬煌'
plt.show()
